---
// About section - connecting to Aloha Publishing
---

<section id="about" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-[var(--color-void)]">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
      <!-- Content -->
      <div data-animate="fade-up">
        <p class="text-[var(--color-coral)] text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">
          About Us
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[var(--color-cream)] mb-6">
          Born from a 
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--color-coral)] to-[var(--color-sunset)] bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            love of storytelling
          </span>
        </h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-6 text-[var(--color-mist)] text-lg leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Aloha Media Studio grew out of a shared love for storytelling. As part of the 
            <a href="https://alohapublishing.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-[var(--color-coral)] hover:text-[var(--color-coral-light)] transition-colors underline underline-offset-4">
              Aloha Publishing
            </a> 
            family, we carry the same heart for story into the world of video, photo, and audio.
          </p>
          <p>
            Our mission is simple: to help people and organizations share meaningful stories through clear, creative, and high-quality media.
          </p>
          <p>
            We believe in <strong class="text-[var(--color-cream)]">clarity first</strong>, 
            <strong class="text-[var(--color-cream)]">creativity with purpose</strong>, and 
            <strong class="text-[var(--color-cream)]">partnership built on trust</strong>. 
            Every project is a collaboration. Our goal is to help you communicate your message clearly and confidently.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Values -->
        <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[var(--color-coral)] mb-2">10+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-stone)]">Years Combined Experience</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[var(--color-coral)] mb-2">50+</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-stone)]">Projects Delivered</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[var(--color-coral)] mb-2">100%</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-[var(--color-stone)]">Aloha Spirit</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Visual -->
      <div class="relative" data-animate="fade-up" data-animate-delay="0.2">
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
          <img 
            src="/images/studio/studio-interior-1.jpg" 
            alt="Inside Aloha Media Studio" 
            class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-[var(--color-void)]/60 to-transparent"></div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Floating accent -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-6 -left-6 w-48 h-48 bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-coral)]/20 to-[var(--color-sunset)]/10 rounded-2xl -z-10 blur-xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute -top-6 -right-6 w-32 h-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-[var(--color-gold)]/20 to-transparent rounded-full -z-10 blur-2xl"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
